      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously preserved. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains in pristine state, still smelling like new with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been garage-kept and maintained with the utmost care. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who expects a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the dealership floor.",
